//      import a static map — `deriveAttention` receives catalog rows), and
//   2. the migration-equivalence BASELINE: the recommendation-catalog seed test
//      asserts the SEEDED rows (read from a migrated DB and mapped) deep-equal
//      these, proving the static map's content survived the migration verbatim
//      and produces identical recs (tests/recommendation-catalog.test.ts).
//
// Content copied from the retired src/lib/coaching-recommendations.ts. Every
// row's `required_signals` is the closed-vocabulary encoding of the exact
// gating the static evaluator applied inline (measured · normalized < 40 ·
// weight ≥ 0.2). `id` = the stable rec id (== rec_interaction_state.rec_id);
// `slug` = the ScoreSlug the component belongs to.
